LUVO
Be good to you.
Chef John Mitchell
Luvo's Chief Innovation Officer,
graduate of the Culinary Institute
of America, and member of the
James Beard Foundation
Good food changes
everything.
We want to change the world. Too big a dream for a small
food company? We don't think so. Not when a little thing like a
healthier choice in a place you don't expect it —a small
delight discovered at 35,000 feet, for instance-can change
your day for the better. Luvo is committed to making food
that tastes great and is good for you and the planet available
wherever you are. Our friends at Delta Air Lines agree and
that's why they've invited us to bring you delicious, nutritious
choices up here, so you can keep the good going on the
ground. And help us change the world, one meal at a time.
We hope you enjoy.
Find Luvo online and at grocery stores nationwide.
Share a photo using # LuvolnFlight for a chance
to win a 1-month supply of entrées.
For official rules visit luvoinc.com/luvoinflight
